messages.msg: Welcome to our site! If you are looking for prayer or someone to chat with, reply to this message or email us at prayer@fightlust.com

I want to stop lusting and committing sexual sin I break all agreements with Satan in regards to sexual sin and I send them to the feet of Jesus to deal with as he sees fit I ask Jesus to forgive me for any way I have agreed with Satan in regards to sexual sin and I ask heaven to break all those agreements I pray for spiritual eyes and spiritual enlightenment to see sin as Jesus sees it and to hate it the way he does I pray for all practice of sexual sin to leave my soul and never come back
